## 1. Token definitions

### Code (today)

Tokens live in **`src/app/theme/`** and compile to runtime CSS:

```css
/* src/app/styles.css â€” import order matters */
@layer reset, theme, base, astryx-base, astryx-theme, components, utilities;

@import "tailwindcss/theme.css" layer(theme);
@import "tailwindcss/preflight.css" layer(base);
@import "@astryxdesign/core/reset.css";
@import "@astryxdesign/core/astryx.css";
@import "./theme/manared.css";
@import "./theme/manared-extensions.css";
@import "@astryxdesign/core/tailwind-theme.css";
@import "tailwindcss/utilities.css" layer(utilities);
```

- **Format:** CSS custom properties (`--color-background-surface`, `--spacing-4`, `--radius-container`)
- **Colour source:** `manaredColourMap.ts` â†’ `manaredTheme.ts` â†’ `vp run build:theme` â†’ `manared.css`
- **Transformation:** `tailwind-theme.css` + `manared-extensions.css` map vars â†’ Tailwind v4 utilities
- **Runtime theme:** `src/app/providers.tsx` wraps `<Theme theme={manaredTheme}>`
- **HTML marker:** `data-astryx-theme="manared"` on `<html>` in `src/app/document.tsx`
- **No `tailwind.config.*`** â€” Tailwind v4 is CSS-first via `vite.config.ts` + `@tailwindcss/vite`

**Three-tier utility mapping:**

| Tier | Examples | When |
| ---- | -------- | ---- |
| Astryx bridge | `bg-body`, `text-primary`, `border-strong` | Standard semantic roles |
| MaNaReD extensions | `bg-body-secondary`, `bg-sidebar`, `text-tertiary`, `border-emphasized`, `bg-chip-active` | MaNaReD-only Figma roles |
| Escape hatch | `bg-[var(--color-*)]` | Last resort |

Discover token values locally:

```bash
vp run astryx -- docs tokens
vp run astryx -- docs theme
vp run build:theme
vp run validate:theme
```

